        "description": "<p>A simple plugin allows you display related posts of post you are viewing</p>\n<p>Shortcode [c4d-related-post image_size=&#8221;thumbnail&#8221; cols=&#8221;3&#8243; count=&#8221;3&#8243;][/c4d-related-post]</p>\n<p>List Params:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>image_size</strong>: thumbnail. Set image size of post.</li>\n<li><strong>cols</strong>: The posts will be showed in row with number column you want.</li>\n<li><strong>count</strong>: The number of post will be showed</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To use full features, please install and active C4D Plugin Manager and Redux Framework</p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"sss9FNJRSJ\"><p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/c4d-plugin-manager/\" rel=\"ugc\">C4D Plugin Manager</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" title=\"&#8220;C4D Plugin Manager&#8221; &#8212; Plugin Directory\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/c4d-plugin-manager/embed/#?secret=dyt0is6yN0#?secret=sss9FNJRSJ\" data-secret=\"sss9FNJRSJ\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"PBSbzDrXqw\"><p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/redux-framework/\" rel=\"ugc\">Redux Framework</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" title=\"&#8220;Redux Framework&#8221; &#8212; Plugin Directory\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/redux-framework/embed/#?secret=57lNJKS0GZ#?secret=PBSbzDrXqw\" data-secret=\"PBSbzDrXqw\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<p>This plugin is used in C4D Vision &#8211; Responsive  WooCommerce Theme</p>\n<p>You can view here http://coffee4dev.com/responsive-woocommerce-theme-c4d-vision/</p>\n",
